@page "/info"
@inherits LayoutComponentBase

<PageTitle>About - PurplePete Chatbot</PageTitle>

<div class="info-container">
    <h1>Welcome to PurplePete</h1>
    <p>
        PurplePete is your friendly chatbot assistant, here to help you with all your questions and tasks. Whether you're looking for quick answers or need assistance navigating through information, PurplePete is here to provide engaging and helpful responses.
    </p>

    <h2>What Can PurplePete Do?</h2>
    <p>
        PurplePete is powered by advanced AI and designed to make your interaction as smooth and natural as possible. Some of the features you can enjoy with PurplePete include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Instant Answers:</strong> Get quick responses to your questions and requests, just like chatting with a friend.</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Typing:</strong> Watch as PurplePete types out responses in real time, mimicking a human conversation.</li>
        <li><strong>Engaging Avatar:</strong> PurplePete's robot avatar changes to match the mood of the conversation, making your interaction even more fun!</li>
        <li><strong>Confluence Knowledge Integration:</strong> PurplePete can access vast amounts of information to help answer more detailed questions, including data from Confluence (a business knowledge base system).</li>
        <li><strong>Future Updates:</strong> Soon, PurplePete will be even smarter with advanced features powered by LLama3, offering more intelligent and tailored responses.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Use PurplePete?</h2>
    <p>
        PurplePete isn’t just another chatbot. It's a powerful assistant designed to help you with tasks, provide answers, and even entertain you along the way. Whether you’re looking for answers, help navigating through processes, or just want to chat, PurplePete makes your experience more efficient and enjoyable.
    </p>
    <p>
        And don’t worry, PurplePete is constantly learning and improving to provide better responses and smarter insights as we roll out new features.
    </p>

    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <p>
        To start chatting with PurplePete, simply type your message in the chat box and let the conversation begin. No need for any special setup — just type and PurplePete will respond instantly.
    </p>

    <h2>Stay Tuned!</h2>
    <p>
        We are always working to improve PurplePete and add new features to make your experience even better. Keep an eye out for future updates and enhancements!
    </p>
</div>
